connecting_rod_length = 10.5 * ureg.cm
connecting_rod_cross_section = 1 * ureg.cm**2
piston_mass = 0.3 * ureg.kilogram
engine_displacement   = 206  # [cc]
compression_ratio     = 6
bore                  = 65.1 * ureg.mm
stroke                = 61.8 * ureg.mm
FA_ratio              = 1/14.7
n_p = 2 * ureg.revolution
R = (connecting_rod_length.to(ureg.mm))/(stroke/2)
otto_eff              = 51.16

Engine Parameters Functions¶

In [33]:
def brake_power(throttle):
    oil_flow_rate = throttle['Oil_Flow_Rate'].values * (ureg.gallon / ureg.min)
    oil_pressure = throttle['Oil_Pressure'].values * (ureg.psi)
    W_dot_b = (oil_flow_rate*oil_pressure)/pump_efficiency
    return W_dot_b.to(ureg.horsepower)

def fuel_consumption(throttle):
    m_dot_f = (throttle['Difference'].values / 30) * (ureg.gram / ureg.second)
    return m_dot_f.to(ureg.pound / ureg.hour)

def bsfc(throttle):
    fc = fuel_consumption(throttle)
    bp = brake_power(throttle)
    bsfc = fc/bp
    return bsfc

def brake_torque(throttle):
    bp = brake_power(throttle)
    bmep = brake_mean_effective_pressure(throttle)
    torque = (bmep * V_d)/(n_p)
    return torque.to(ureg.lbf * ureg.foot)

def volumetric_efficiency(throttle):
    fc = fuel_consumption(throttle)
    m_dot_a = fc.to(ureg.pound / ureg.minute)/FA_ratio
    N = get_rpm(throttle)
    vol_eff = (m_dot_a*n_p)/(air_density*V_d*N)
    return vol_eff.to_base_units()

def brake_mean_effective_pressure(throttle):
    bp = brake_power(throttle)
    N = get_rpm(throttle)
    bmep = (bp*n_p)/(V_d*N)
    return bmep.to(ureg.psi)

def cycle_efficiency(throttle):
    bp = brake_power(throttle).to(ureg.kilowatts)
    fc = fuel_consumption(throttle).to(ureg.kilogram / ureg.hour)
    high_heat_fuel = higher_heating_value
    cycle_eff = bp/(fc * high_heat_fuel)
    return cycle_eff

def get_rpm(throttle):
    rpm = throttle['RPM'].values * ureg.rpm
    return rpm

def average_piston_speed(rpm):
    U_p_avg = 2*stroke.to(ureg.meter)*((rpm/60) * ureg.rps)
    return U_p_avg.to(ureg.meter / ureg.second)

def instantaneous_piston_speed(rpm):
    U_p = average_piston_speed(rpm)*((math.pi/2)*np.sin(theta)*(1+(np.cos(theta)/(np.sqrt(R**2-np.sin(theta)**2)))))
    return U_p

def instantaneous_piston_acceleration(rpm):
    a = stroke/2
    l = connecting_rod_length.to(ureg.mm)
    x_2_prime = -a*np.cos(theta)\
                -((a**2*(np.cos(theta)**2-np.sin(theta)**2))/(np.sqrt(l**2-(a**2*np.sin(theta)**2))))\
                -((a**4*np.sin(theta)**2*np.cos(theta)**2)/(np.sqrt(l**2-(a**2*np.sin(theta)**2)))**3)
    A_p = x_2_prime*((math.pi*2*rpm)/60)*ureg.rps**2
    return A_p.to(ureg.meter / ureg.second**2)

def connecting_rod_tensile_stress(rpm):
    mass = piston_mass
    accel = instantaneous_piston_acceleration(rpm)
    F = mass*accel
    A = connecting_rod_cross_section.to(ureg.meter**2)
    stress = F/A
    return stress.to(ureg.megapascal)

connecting_rod_tensile_stress(2900).max()
Out[33]:
0.020051406701204953 megapascal

Plot Brake Horsepower¶

In [13]:
plt.rcParams['figure.dpi']= 150
fig, ax = plt.subplots()

smoothing_constant = 3
x = get_rpm(full_throttle).magnitude
x_smooth =  np.linspace(x.min(),x.max(),300)

y1 = brake_power(full_throttle).magnitude
y2 = brake_power(one_quarter_throttle).magnitude

sp1 = make_interp_spline(x, y1, k=smoothing_constant)
sp2 = make_interp_spline(x, y2, k=smoothing_constant)

y1_smooth = sp1(x_smooth)
y2_smooth = sp2(x_smooth)

ax.plot(x_smooth,y1_smooth, label='Full Throttle')
ax.plot(get_rpm(three_quater_throttle).magnitude,brake_power(three_quater_throttle).magnitude,'.', label='Three Quarter Throttle')
ax.plot(get_rpm(one_half_throttle).magnitude,brake_power(one_half_throttle).magnitude,'.', label='One Half Throttle')
ax.plot(x_smooth,y2_smooth, label='One Quarter Throttle')

ax.set_title('Brake Horsepower')
ax.set_xlabel('RPM')
ax.set_ylabel('Brake Horsepower')

legend = ax.legend(loc='lower center',bbox_to_anchor=(.5, -.35), shadow=True, ncol=2)
ax.grid()
